";; appendix-01-bach-goldberg.slat
;; Book of Music — Appendix 1: Bach and the Goldberg Variations
;; Written 2026-07-13. Author: Lacuna Labs Engineering.
;; Doctrine: publishable prose · no hallucination · analysis-shape.
;; Real work: Johann Sebastian Bach, Aria mit verschiedenen Veränderungen
;; ('Aria with Diverse Variations'), BWV 988, published Nuremberg 1741,
;; second part of the Clavier-Übung. PD.
;; Nickname 'Goldberg Variations' comes from a story told by Johann Nikolaus
